Images: ["[1-1687327995.png](https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-1687327995.png)", "[1-1687328062.jpg](https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-1687328062.jpg)", "[1-1687328140.jpg](https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-1687328140.jpg)", "[1-1687328233.jpg](https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-1687328233.jpg)"]

